  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "18 months, I was-- I don't know whether I call it-- just-- They want me to-- to take to the officer's school, but I don't want to, because I was not happy with it-- with all-- discipline and everything.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was hating it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What was your rank?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just-- I don't know how to call it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just a soldier.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't even accepted the capital, what they want from me, because you have to be leader, and leader have to be rather following the orders for-- for-- for the [INAUDIBLE] and so on.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No, I didn't agree with something, and I don't want to be the-- the leader.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I was treated rather good, but there was-- in '35, some kind of [INAUDIBLE]-- some type-- some [INAUDIBLE], and there was very bad going on, things.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But one of the-- the-- they want to take [INAUDIBLE] will be, he was the commander of the 6th Division.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He took command of the military.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was a-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] there was a written [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] what-- what soldier can do, what have to do, all that [? no. ?] Between that one was that Jewish people or people from the same state would-- would-- have to be the-- the army assistant can be excused from the duty.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So where we been staying in-- in front of the door, I have to step out three fee-- three feet, or three steps.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this-- this [INAUDIBLE] who is-- who was the head of the company asked, what are you doing?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I ask-- I tell him, I am from Krakow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I have to be excused.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The next answer was, Jewish and people who are from Krakow, step out.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
